ipsoSystem.name: ipsoSystem

revisions.description: Author: Shoba Narasimhan Panappakkam Revision 1.03 Added ipsoNotificationGroup. Added 5 system traps. - 10.20.1999
Author: Kripakaran karlekar Revision 1.04 SMIv1 to SMIv2 MIB conversion - 11.01.2000
Author: Rupa Bose Revision 1.05 Added Asset Mib - 7.16.01

ipsoSystem.contactinfo: Alan Fransisco Shoba Narasimhan Panappakkam Kripakaran Karlekar Postal: 313 Fairchild Drive Mountain View, California, 94043
ipsoSystem.description: Author: Alan Fransisco Revision 1.02 changed ipsoChassisMBType to DisplayString - 09.11.1998 removed ipsoChassisType - 20.08.1998 removed ipsoFanSpeed - 19.08.1998 removed ipsoCardStorageCapacity and made other corrections - 12.08.1998 Added Nokia Telecommunications header - 03.08.1998

ipsoChassisGroup.name: ipsoChassisGroup
ipsoChassisGroup.description: A collection of objects providing the instrumentation of ipsoChassis

ipsoChassisSerialNumber.name: ipsoChassisSerialNumber
ipsoChassisSerialNumber.description: The serial number of this device.

ipsoChassisMBType.name: ipsoChassisMBType
ipsoChassisMBType.description: An string value representing the type of motherboard populating this device.

ipsoChassisMBRevNumber.name: ipsoChassisMBRevNumber
ipsoChassisMBRevNumber.description: The revision number for the motherboard of this chassis.

ipsoChassisMBSerialNumber.name: ipsoChassisMBSerialNumber
ipsoChassisMBSerialNumber.description: The serial number for the motherboard of this chassis.

ipsoChassisTemperature.name: ipsoChassisTemperature
ipsoChassisTemperature.description: An indication of whether or not the internal temperature reading of this chassis is higher than the recommended operating temperature.

ipsoCardTable.name: ipsoCardTable
ipsoCardTable.description: A table of slots or onboard network interfaces in the chassis.

ipsoCardEntry.name: ipsoCardEntry
ipsoCardEntry.description: A sequence of slot entries containing the operational status, and ifType (if applicable) of the slot's module.

ipsoCardIndex.name: ipsoCardIndex
ipsoCardIndex.description: The number of the slot in which this card is plugged.

ipsoCardOperStatus.name: ipsoCardOperStatus
ipsoCardOperStatus.description: The operational status of this card.

ipsoFanGroup.name: ipsoFanGroup
ipsoFanGroup.description: A collection of objects providing the instrumentation of ipsoFanGroup

ipsoFanTable.name: ipsoFanTable
ipsoFanTable.description: A listing of fans which are present in this chassis.

ipsoFanEntry.name: ipsoFanEntry
ipsoFanEntry.description: A grouping of objects displaying certain characteristics of each fan present in the chassis.

ipsoFanIndex.name: ipsoFanIndex
ipsoFanIndex.description: A unique index for this particular fan.

ipsoFanOperStatus.name: ipsoFanOperStatus
ipsoFanOperStatus.description: The operational status of this fan.

ipsoPowerSupplyGroup.name: ipsoPowerSupplyGroup
ipsoPowerSupplyGroup.description: A collection of objects providing the instrumentation of ipsoPowerSupply

ipsoPowerSupplyTable.name: ipsoPowerSupplyTable
ipsoPowerSupplyTable.description: A table of all power supplies installed in this chassis.

ipsoPowerSupplyEntry.name: ipsoPowerSupplyEntry
ipsoPowerSupplyEntry.description: A list of characteristics of each power supply.

ipsoPowerSupplyIndex.name: ipsoPowerSupplyIndex
ipsoPowerSupplyIndex.description: A unique index representing this power supply.

ipsoPowerSupplyOverTemperature.name: ipsoPowerSupplyOverTemperature
ipsoPowerSupplyOverTemperature.description: An indication of whether or not this power supply's internal temperature is over the recommended operation temperature limit.

ipsoPowerSupplyOperStatus.name: ipsoPowerSupplyOperStatus
ipsoPowerSupplyOperStatus.description: The operational status of this power supply.

ipsoConfigGroup.name: ipsoConfigGroup
ipsoConfigGroup.description: A collection of objects providing the instrumentation of ipsoConfigGroup

ipsoConfigTable.name: ipsoConfigTable
ipsoConfigTable.description: A table of available configurations for this system.

ipsoConfigEntry.name: ipsoConfigEntry
ipsoConfigEntry.description: A list of attributes for each available configuration on this system.

ipsoConfigIndex.name: ipsoConfigIndex
ipsoConfigIndex.description: The index for this configuration, with 1 representing the currently running database and traversing from newest to oldest.

ipsoConfigFilePath.name: ipsoConfigFilePath
ipsoConfigFilePath.description: The absolute pathname and filename which holds a record of this configuration, truncated to within 255 characters.

ipsoConfigFileDateAndTime.name: ipsoConfigFileDateAndTime
ipsoConfigFileDateAndTime.description: The date and time of the last time this file was changed.

ipsoConfigLogSize.name: ipsoConfigLogSize
ipsoConfigLogSize.description: A maximum limit on the number of entries which may be recorded in the ipsoConfigLogTable.

ipsoConfigLogTable.name: ipsoConfigLogTable
ipsoConfigLogTable.description: A log of the most recent configuration changes on this system.

ipsoConfigLogEntry.name: ipsoConfigLogEntry
ipsoConfigLogEntry.description: A listing of attributes for a configuration change. This table lists the oldest configuration change in the table and proceeds toward the most recent configuration change.

ipsoConfigLogIndex.name: ipsoConfigLogIndex
ipsoConfigLogIndex.description: The unique index of this configuration change entry.

ipsoConfigLogDescr.name: ipsoConfigLogDescr
ipsoConfigLogDescr.description: A synopsis of the nature of the configuration change.

ipsoImageGroup.name: ipsoImageGroup
ipsoImageGroup.description: A collection of objects providing the instrumentation of ipsoImage Group

ipsoImageTable.name: ipsoImageTable
ipsoImageTable.description: A table of resident kernel images on this system, including the currently up-and-running kernel.

ipsoImageEntry.name: ipsoImageEntry
ipsoImageEntry.description: A series of attributes for each image including date loaded, version number, serial number, etc.

ipsoImageIndex.name: ipsoImageIndex
ipsoImageIndex.description: A unique index for the image represented by this entry. The currently running image has a index value of 1, and subsequent images are indexed from earliest loaded image to most recently loaded image.

ipsoImageVersionNumber.name: ipsoImageVersionNumber
ipsoImageVersionNumber.description: The version number of this image.

ipsoImageSerialNumber.name: ipsoImageSerialNumber
ipsoImageSerialNumber.description: The serial number of this image.

ipsoImageTimeOfLoad.name: ipsoImageTimeOfLoad
ipsoImageTimeOfLoad.description: The date and time when this instance of the image had been first transferred onto this device.

ipsoStorageGroup.name: ipsoStorageGroup
ipsoStorageGroup.description: A collection of objects providing the instrumentation of ipsoStorage Group

ipsoSIMMTotal.name: ipsoSIMMTotal
ipsoSIMMTotal.description: The total memory capacity in megabytes contained in the SIMM sockets.

ipsoProcessGroup.name: ipsoProcessGroup
ipsoProcessGroup.description: A collection of objects providing the instrumentation of ipsoProcessor Group

ipsoProcessorUtilization.name: ipsoProcessorUtilization
ipsoProcessorUtilization.description: The current percentage of CPU utilization.

ipsoProcessTable.name: ipsoProcessTable
ipsoProcessTable.description: A table of all processes currently running on this system.

ipsoProcessEntry.name: ipsoProcessEntry
ipsoProcessEntry.description: A sequence of objects describing each process's execution.

ipsoProcessParentID.name: ipsoProcessParentID
ipsoProcessParentID.description: The ID of this process's parent process.

ipsoProcessOwner.name: ipsoProcessOwner
ipsoProcessOwner.description: The name of the user who is given execution of this process.

ipsoProcessMemory.name: ipsoProcessMemory
ipsoProcessMemory.description: The amount of memory in kilobytes which this process is utilizing in its current execution state.

ipsoProcessPercentCPU.name: ipsoProcessPercentCPU
ipsoProcessPercentCPU.description: The percentage of the CPU cycle which this process is utilizing in its current execution state.

ipsoDiskMirrorGroup.name: ipsoDiskMirrorGroup
ipsoDiskMirrorGroup.description: A collection of objects providing the instrumentation of ipsoDiskMirroring

ipsoTotalDiskMirrorSets.name: ipsoTotalDiskMirrorSets
ipsoTotalDiskMirrorSets.description: The total number of mirror sets currently configured on the system.

ipsoDiskMirrorSetTable.name: ipsoDiskMirrorSetTable
ipsoDiskMirrorSetTable.description: A table of all mirror sets currently on this system.

ipsoDiskMirrorSetEntry.name: ipsoDiskMirrorSetEntry
ipsoDiskMirrorSetEntry.description: A sequence of objects describing each mirror set.

ipsoDiskMirrorSetIndex.name: ipsoDiskMirrorSetIndex
ipsoDiskMirrorSetIndex.description: The mirror set index used to identify a mirror set present on the system.

ipsoDiskMirrorSetSourceDriveIndex.name: ipsoDiskMirrorSetSourceDriveIndex
ipsoDiskMirrorSetSourceDriveIndex.description: The source drive of the mirror set.

ipsoDiskMirrorSetDestinationDriveIndex.name: ipsoDiskMirrorSetDestinationDriveIndex
ipsoDiskMirrorSetDestinationDriveIndex.description: The destination drive of the mirror set.

ipsoDiskMirrorSetSyncPercent.name: ipsoDiskMirrorSetSyncPercent
ipsoDiskMirrorSetSyncPercent.description: The percentage of the space in sync of source drive with the destination drive.

ipsoAssetGroup.name: ipsoAssetGroup
ipsoAssetGroup.description: A collection of objects representing some of the basic assets of the IPSO system.

ipsoAssetChassisSerialNumber.name: ipsoAssetChassisSerialNumber
ipsoAssetChassisSerialNumber.description: The serial number of this device.

ipsoCPUModel.name: ipsoCPUModel
ipsoCPUModel.description: The CPU model of this device.

ipsoCPUMfr.name: ipsoCPUMfr
ipsoCPUMfr.description: The CPU manufacturer of this device.

ipsoKernMaxMem.name: ipsoKernMaxMem
ipsoKernMaxMem.description: The maximum amount of kernel memory.

ipsoMotherBoardSerNum.name: ipsoMotherBoardSerNum
ipsoMotherBoardSerNum.description: The serial number of the motherboard.

ipsoMotherBoardRev.name: ipsoMotherBoardRev
ipsoMotherBoardRev.description: The revision number of the motherboard.

ipsoMotherBoardModel.name: ipsoMotherBoardModel
ipsoMotherBoardModel.description: The model number of the motherboard.

ipsoOSRelease.name: ipsoOSRelease
ipsoOSRelease.description: The release number current IPSO OS.

ipsoOSVersion.name: ipsoOSVersion
ipsoOSVersion.description: The version number of the current IPSO OS.

ipsoProductModel.name: ipsoProductModel
ipsoProductModel.description: The product model number of the current system.

ipsoAssetTable.name: ipsoAssetTable
ipsoAssetTable.description: A table of currently installed packages and their relevant information.

ipsoAssetEntry.name: ipsoAssetEntry
ipsoAssetEntry.description: A sequence of package entries containing the version number, license information and policy type for the particular package.

ipsoPkgIndex.name: ipsoPkgIndex
ipsoPkgIndex.description: The index used to iterate through all packages which are installed and currently running, ie, Checkpoint, ISS, etc.

ipsoPkgMajorVersion.name: ipsoPkgMajorVersion
ipsoPkgMajorVersion.description: The major version number of the package. For FireWall NG, this displays the Build and Feature Pack information.

ipsoPkgMinorVersion.name: ipsoPkgMinorVersion
ipsoPkgMinorVersion.description: The minor version number of the package. For Firewall NG, this is not applicable.

ipsoPkgLicense.name: ipsoPkgLicense
ipsoPkgLicense.description: The license information of the package.

ipsoDiskDriveTable.name: ipsoDiskDriveTable
ipsoDiskDriveTable.description: A table of all disk drives currently on this system.

ipsoDiskDriveEntry.name: ipsoDiskDriveEntry
ipsoDiskDriveEntry.description: A sequence of objects describing each disk drive.

ipsoDiskDriveIndex.name: ipsoDiskDriveIndex
ipsoDiskDriveIndex.description: The drive index used to identify a particular row in table.

ipsoSysDiskDriveIndex.name: ipsoSysDiskDriveIndex
ipsoSysDiskDriveIndex.description: The drive index used internally by the system to identify a disk.

ipsoDiskDriveModel.name: ipsoDiskDriveModel
ipsoDiskDriveModel.description: The model of the disk drive.

ipsoDiskDriveCapacity.name: ipsoDiskDriveCapacity
ipsoDiskDriveCapacity.description: The total data holding capacity of the disk drive.

ipsoDiskDriveLocation.name: ipsoDiskDriveLocation
ipsoDiskDriveLocation.description: The location of the disk drive.

ipsoLicenseGroup.name: ipsoLicenseGroup
ipsoLicenseGroup.description: A collection of objects sent as a part of license trap.

ipsoFeatureName.name: ipsoFeatureName
ipsoFeatureName.description: The feature name that is licensed.

ipsoDaysToExpire.name: ipsoDaysToExpire
ipsoDaysToExpire.description: Number of Day(s) for the license to expire, the value of this object is zero, if the license for feature has expired.

ipsoNotificationGroup.name: ipsoNotificationGroup
ipsoNotificationGroup.description: A collection of notifications providing the instrumentation of ipsoNotification

systemTrapConfigurationChange.name: systemTrapConfigurationChange
systemTrapConfigurationChange.description: The trap which indicates a temporary configuration change.

systemTrapConfigurationFileChange.name: systemTrapConfigurationFileChange
systemTrapConfigurationFileChange.description: The trap which indicates a change in the configuration file.

systemTrapConfigurationSaveChange.name: systemTrapConfigurationSaveChange
systemTrapConfigurationSaveChange.description: The trap which indicates a permanent configuration change which is written to the configuration file.

systemTrapLowDiskSpace.name: systemTrapLowDiskSpace
systemTrapLowDiskSpace.description: The trap which indicates if the disk space is low.

systemTrapNoDiskSpace.name: systemTrapNoDiskSpace
systemTrapNoDiskSpace.description: The trap which indicates that there is no more disk space available.

systemTrapDiskFailure.name: systemTrapDiskFailure
systemTrapDiskFailure.description: The trap which indicates that a particular disk drive has failed , means giving no response for read/write operation.

systemTrapDiskMirrorSetCreate.name: systemTrapDiskMirrorSetCreate
systemTrapDiskMirrorSetCreate.description: The trap which indicates that a particular mirror set has been created on the system.

systemTrapDiskMirrorSetDelete.name: systemTrapDiskMirrorSetDelete
systemTrapDiskMirrorSetDelete.description: The trap which indicates that a particular mirror set has been deleted from the system.

systemTrapSnmpProcessShutdown.name: systemTrapSnmpProcessShutdown
systemTrapSnmpProcessShutdown.description: The trap which indicates that the snmp process is going down.

systemTrapDiskMirrorSyncFailure.name: systemTrapDiskMirrorSyncFailure
systemTrapDiskMirrorSyncFailure.description: The trap which indicates that a particular mirror set sync has failed.

systemTrapDiskMirrorSyncSuccess.name: systemTrapDiskMirrorSyncSuccess
systemTrapDiskMirrorSyncSuccess.description: The trap which indicates that a particular mirror set sync has succeeded.

systemTrapLicense.name: systemTrapLicense
systemTrapLicense.description: The trap indicates the product is about to expire/expired. A zero value for the NoOfDays means the product has expired.
